gg halo gold

This is a small Gun Game map with a Halo Theme. Enjoy! This map has Buy Zones for non-GG play also.

-	48 Spawns
-       Buy Zones
-	Nav file for bots
-	Overview Radar Map
-	Cube Maps
-	Optimized with No Draw for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat
-	Custom Textures from [-B-]
-	Custom Skybox from [-B-]
